    <li> <a href="http://web.stcloudstate.edu/aanda/cs201/Gaddis/7e/Labs/SourceCode/Lab4/LogicalOp.cpp">LogicalOp.cpp</a>
    <li> <a href="http://web.stcloudstate.edu/aanda/cs201/Gaddis/7e/Labs/SourceCode/Lab4/switch.cpp">switch.cpp</a>
</ul>
</code>

